<br>
Therefore, please make specific proposed PoP pet heals in this thread.<br>
<br>
Please try to explain why you think your proposal is appropriate.  Explain how it is intended to be used, and try to consider how it could be abused.  Please limit yourself to new 61+ PoP spells.<br>
<br>
To get the ball rolling, here are my ideas.  A PoP pet heal would have to be higher level, 65ish, as there is already a 60 pet heal.  If the purpose of the heal is to save your pet from death, then in order to be better at saving your pet than a nuke, it has be be a near-substitute for mend companion or complete heal, although not as good as either.  In order to keep it from being overpowering, it should have a high cost.<br>
<br>
Therefore, I would propose something like a complete pet heal with a star ruby as a component.  It would allow you to save your pet in emergencies at a cost, and would not obsolete Mend Companion.  Star rubies cost 60 pp each, and already used by mages for Banishment, which in a way is the opposite of pet complete heal.  I think pearl would be too cheap.<br>
<br>
I am sure there are plenty of other ideas quite different from this one.<br>
<br>
